Is he still in love with his ex?He s just not ready to commit himself to you. Whenever you try to bring up the status of your relationship during conversations, he s going to shy away from it because he doesn t want to give you a definitive answer. He doesn t want to tie himself down to you just yet because deep down, he s still entertaining the possibility of getting back together with his ex. He s only treating you as if you re a second option.&nbsp;&nbsp;